                            <h4>Why do I need to register my car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                In case you plan to be just a passenger who is using the application just for looking for rides and not for creating them, there is no need
                                for you to register your car. In the other case, when you also want to be the one who is driving the other people to their destinations, to create
                                the ride offers there is a need to have a car registered in your profile. Without it, it will not allow you to create a ride because no plate number will
                                be available in the list which is a required field in the form.
                            </p>

                            <h4>What is needed for registering my car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To register a car, you need to be logged in and  registered as a user. 
                                Except for this step, in the registration form are fields like brand, model, number of seats and number plate which are necessary to fill.
                                To get to the Registration form, please check the  "How to register a car"  question.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to register a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                Before registering your car, you need to be  logged in or create a new profile. The first way how to register a car is to follow the link on the account activation page, where you land clicking the link in the confirmation email. After logging in you will be redirected to the car registration form.
                                Here you can fill all the information and click on "Create" button. The car will immediately appear in your list of cars.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                The other way is, when you are just logged in as a user, you need to open your personal "profile page" by clicking on your name up on the right side.
                                On this page you can see "My cars" option in which there is a button for creating a new car. 
                                After clicking on the button, you are redirected to the  registration form for cars.
                                In case you decide not to create the car, you can click on "Back to My Cars" link under the registration form.
                                As soon as you "save" all the information, the car is created and shown in your list of cars. The required fields details when registering a car are: 
                                "Brand, Model, Number of seats and number plate.""
                          
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                In case you are still completely lost and have no idea how to access the registration form, here is the link! (You will need to log in first, in case you aren't yet)
                                <br />
                                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/CreateCar">Create a car</a>
                            </p>

                            <h4>Where can I see my registered cars?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have at least one car created. Just open your personal profile page by clicking on
                                your name up on the right side. On this page you can see "My cars" option on the left side. 
                                Here you will see all the cars you have registered shown in a list.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to edit a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have the car created to edit it.
                                To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on your name up on the right side.
                                On this page you can see "My cars" option on the left side in which the list of cars registered by you is shown.
                                On the right side of each car in the end of the line is the option for Editing the car "The edit button is blue icon with a pen on it".
                                After clicking on the blue button with pen the page for editing is opened. Be careful to choose the right car you want to edit.
                                To make sure  you choose the right one, all the information is displayed on this Edit Page.
                                If you find out you do not want to edit  this one car, you can easily click on the "Back to My Cars" link in the end of the editing form,  and choose the right car.
                                If you are sure you want to edit this car, write the new information where it is needed and click on the "Save" button in the end  of the form.
                                After this action the list of your cars is displayed again with all the new information.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to delete a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have the car created to delete it.
                                To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on your name up on the right side.
                                On this page you can see "My cars" option on the left side, where all the cars you have registered are shown in a list.
                                On the right side of each car at the end of the line is the option for Deleting the car.
                                After clicking on the red button with  a trash can the page for deleting is open.
                                Be careful to choose the right car you want to delete.
                                To make sure you choose the right one, all the information is displayed on this Delete Page.
                                If you find out you do not want to delete  this precise  car, you can easily click on the "Back to My Cars" link at the end,  and choose the right car.
                                If you are sure you want to delete this precise car, click on the red "Delete" button. 
                               After this action, the list of your cars is displayed again. 
                               The deleted car is not displayed. Neither is the  create a ride button visible. 
                               After you delete a car,  all bookings and rides connected to this car are also deleted.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <b>!!! Deleting a car deletes everything attached to that car i.e rides and bookings!!!</b>
                            </p>
