                                    </p>

                                    <h4>What can be found on my profile?</h4>
                                    <p>
                                        On your profile page you can see your personal information as well as all your cars, bookings, rides and reviews.
                                        You can also change your password here or delete your account.
                                    </p>

                                    <h4>Who can see my profile?</h4>
                                    <p>
                                        Just the drivers whose rides you booked can check your profile.
                                        No one else has access to your profile.
                                    </p>

                                    <h4>What can others see about me?</h4>
